README.codes
============

This is a brief description of the codes in this directory.

ring.chpl : Communicate around a ring with blocking sends/receives.
simple_mixed.chpl : Simple example of a mixed Chapel+MPI code.
test_rank_locale_equal.chpl : Verify that CHPL_COMM_WORLD has the correct ordering.
transpose.chpl : Do a distributed matrix transpose using AlltoAll and Chapel code.
test_mpi.chpl : Exercise the C_API. There is a .good and a .prediff file for this.
